---
title: Stir-Fried Mushrooms & Veggies with Garlic Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: Stir-fries are a fun way to get all those veggies in one go. There’s two types of mushrooms, Asian greens and carrot
tossed through a darkly indulgent soy sauce and stir-fry sauce. The sauces will soak into the rice so nothing is missed
when you dig in tonight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
